question: keyphrases used by Luke S Zettlemoyer for each year
query: SELECT DISTINCT t2.keyphraseid, t3.year FROM paper AS t3 JOIN paperkeyphrase AS t2 ON t3.paperid = t2.paperid JOIN writes AS t4 ON t4.paperid = t3.paperid JOIN author AS t1 ON t4.authorid = t1.authorid WHERE t1.authorname = 'Luke S Zettlemoyer' ORDER BY t3.year NULLS FIRST, t2.keyphraseid NULLS FIRST
